org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel

Enum TextAutofit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TextAutofit>
      • org.apache.poi.xssf.usermodel.TextAutofit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TextAutofit> 

    public enum TextAutofit
extends java.lang.Enum<TextAutofit>
    Specifies a list of auto-fit types.

    Autofit specifies that a shape should be auto-fit to fully contain the text described within it. Auto-fitting is when text within a shape is scaled in order to contain all the text inside

    (指定自动调整类型列表。自动调整指定形状应自动调整以完全包含其中描述的文本。自动调整是指缩放形状内的文本以包含其中的所有文本)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      NONE
      Specifies that text within the text body should not be auto-fit to the bounding box.(指定文本正文中的文本不应自动调整到边框。)
      NORMAL
      Specifies that text within the text body should be normally auto-fit to the bounding box.(指定文本正文中的文本通常应自动调整到边框。)
      SHAPE
      Specifies that a shape should be auto-fit to fully contain the text described within it.(指定形状应自动调整以完全包含其中描述的文本。)

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NONE

        public static final TextAutofit NONE
        Specifies that text within the text body should not be auto-fit to the bounding box. Auto-fitting is when text within a text box is scaled in order to remain inside the text box.(指定文本正文中的文本不应自动调整到边框。自动调整是指缩放文本框中的文本以保留在文本框中。)

      • NORMAL

        public static final TextAutofit NORMAL
        Specifies that text within the text body should be normally auto-fit to the bounding box. Autofitting is when text within a text box is scaled in order to remain inside the text box.

        Example: Consider the situation where a user is building a diagram and needs to have the text for each shape that they are using stay within the bounds of the shape. An easy way this might be done is by using NORMAL autofit

        (指定文本正文中的文本通常应自动调整到边框。自动调整是指缩放文本框中的文本以保留在文本框中。示例：考虑这样的情况：用户正在构建图表，并且需要让他们正在使用的每个形状的文本保持在形状的界限内。实现这一目标的一种简单方法是使用NORMAL autofit)

      • SHAPE

        public static final TextAutofit SHAPE
        Specifies that a shape should be auto-fit to fully contain the text described within it. Auto-fitting is when text within a shape is scaled in order to contain all the text inside.

        Example: Consider the situation where a user is building a diagram and needs to have the text for each shape that they are using stay within the bounds of the shape. An easy way this might be done is by using SHAPE autofit

        (指定形状应自动调整以完全包含其中描述的文本。自动调整是指缩放形状内的文本以包含其中的所有文本。示例：考虑这样的情况：用户正在构建图表，并且需要让他们正在使用的每个形状的文本保持在形状的界限内。实现这一目标的一种简单方法是使用SHADE autofit)
